' ─── User interactions ───
user --> IR : speaks / types
user --> Dash : browse sessions
user --> LP : public tools

' ─── Frontend internal ───
App --> Auth : reads user
App --> IR : renders interview
App --> Dash : renders dashboard
App --> AR : renders report
App --> AV : renders analytics
App --> LP : renders landing
IR --> STT : voice input
IR --> TTS : voice output
IR --> AC : api.respond()
AR --> AC : api.getReport()
AV --> AC : api.getAnalyticsBenchmark()
Dash --> SB_FE : select sessions
IPT --> AC : generatePrepQuestions()
ATS --> AC : checkATS()
Auth --> SB_FE : signIn/signUp/signOut
AC --> SB_FE : token refresh (401)

' ─── API layer → Backend ───
AC --> Main : HTTP/REST (Bearer JWT)
STT --> Main : POST /transcribe (audio blob)

' ─── Backend internal ───
Main --> Graph : invoke(state, config)
Main --> SB_BE : log/read/save sessions
Graph --> Nodes : orchestrates
Graph --> Edges : routing
Nodes --> Prompts : get_system_prompt(mode)
Nodes --> Rubrics : get_rubric_prompt(mode)
Nodes --> Groq : LLM calls
Groq --> GROQ_API : HTTP API

' ─── External auth ───
AC --> SUPA_AUTH : JWT issued here
SB_FE --> SUPA_AUTH : auth ops
Main --> SUPA_AUTH : JWT verification

' ─── Database ───
SB_BE --> SUPA : REST API (sessions, assessments)

